agentRadiusAccountingMode.description: Identifies if RADIUS Accounting has been enabled or not

agentRadiusStatsClear.name: agentRadiusStatsClear
agentRadiusStatsClear.description: When set to enable(1), all Radius statistics will be reset.

agentRadiusAccountingIndexNextValid.name: agentRadiusAccountingIndexNextValid
agentRadiusAccountingIndexNextValid.description: Indicates the next valid index into the agentRadiusAccountingConfigTable for creation. If no additional entries are allowed, this will be 0.

agentRadiusAccountingConfigTable.name: agentRadiusAccountingConfigTable
agentRadiusAccountingConfigTable.description: Table with information about Radius Accounting Server IP Addresses, port numbers and shared secret. Only one entry is supported at this time.

agentRadiusAccountingConfigEntry.name: agentRadiusAccountingConfigEntry
agentRadiusAccountingConfigEntry.description: Entry consisting of configuration data for a Radius Accounting Server.

agentRadiusAccountingServerIndex.name: agentRadiusAccountingServerIndex
agentRadiusAccountingServerIndex.description: Unique index of the configured RADIUS accounting server. The next valid value of this object for creation is specified by agentRadiusAccountingIndexNextValid.

agentRadiusAccountingServerAddress.name: agentRadiusAccountingServerAddress
agentRadiusAccountingServerAddress.description: IP Address of the configured RADIUS accounting server. This object cannot be changed after creation.

agentRadiusAccountingServerAddressType.name: agentRadiusAccountingServerAddressType
agentRadiusAccountingServerAddressType.description: IP Address Type of the configured RADIUS accounting server. This object cannot be changed after creation.

agentRadiusAccountingPort.name: agentRadiusAccountingPort
agentRadiusAccountingPort.description: Port number for the RADIUS accounting server.

agentRadiusAccountingSecret.name: agentRadiusAccountingSecret
agentRadiusAccountingSecret.description: Configured shared sercret for the RADIUS accounting server.

agentRadiusAccountingStatus.name: agentRadiusAccountingStatus
agentRadiusAccountingStatus.description: Creates or destroys a RADIUS accounting server entry. During creation, the next available index is specified by the agentRadiusAccountingIndexNextValid object. Rows creation using a different value for agentRadiusAccountingServerIndex will fail. active(1) - This entry is active. createAndGo(4) - Creates a new entry. destroy(6) - Deletes an entry.

agentRadiusAccountingServerName.name: agentRadiusAccountingServerName
agentRadiusAccountingServerName.description: Configured identification name for the RADIUS Accounting server.

agentRadiusServerIndexNextValid.name: agentRadiusServerIndexNextValid

agentRadiusServerConfigTable.description: Table with information about Radius Authentication Server IP Addresses, port numbers and shared secret

agentRadiusServerConfigEntry.name: agentRadiusServerConfigEntry
agentRadiusServerConfigEntry.description: Entry consisting of configuration data for a Radius Authentication Server.

agentRadiusServerIndex.name: agentRadiusServerIndex

agentRadiusServerAddress.name: agentRadiusServerAddress
